MR project summary
==================

MR is a Turbo Vision editor project inspired by classic Multi-Edit.
The current code focuses on a stable DOS-like workflow and clean
incremental reconstruction.

Current highlights
------------------
- Multi-Edit style menu and status line.
- In-memory macro compiler and VM.
- Block, search, and window operations.
- WINDOW LIST dialog with real actions.
- Room for later piece-table and Tree-sitter work.

Near-term direction
-------------------
Complete the remaining menu commands, improve editor persistence,
and keep macro, menu, and UI behavior aligned.
